snippet.title: Minecraft Festive Mash Up 2016 now available on Pocket / Win 10
snippet.description: Tear off the wrapping paper and dig into this big box of festive treats! Wander through a winter wonderland and enjoy new textures, skins and more! Find out about it here: https://minecraft.net/en/article/festive-mash-2016-here
